Package: GeoFunPhy
Title: Analysis of Ecological and Evolutionary Rarity Status
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Imports: Rdpack, ape, dplyr, tidyr, stringr, rgbif, rgl, magrittr, purrr, treeio, vegan, datasets, base, dbscan, foreach, doParallel, sf, tibble, utils, future, future.apply, geojsonio, ggplot2, leaflet, picante, rmapshaper
