Description: EcoStatusR calculates measures of range size, evolutionary distinctiveness, and functional trait distinctiveness to classify the eco-evolutionary rarity status of species. Ecological status can be used to infer associated organismal strategy. GeoFunPhy also allows users to utilize their own data to determine the ecological status of species of interest.
